---

## üõ†Ô∏è Technical Stack

This project represents a custom **headless** implementation of Demucs:

- **Frontend:** HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript (GitHub Pages)
- **Audio Visualization:** [WaveSurfer.js](https://wavesurfer-js.org/)
- **Backend API:** Python Flask
- **Tunneling:** Ngrok (secure public access)
- **AI Engine:** PyTorch + Demucs

---

## ‚ñ∂Ô∏è How to Use

1. Visit the web app: https://vicsanity623.github.io  
2. **Drag & Drop** your audio file (MP3, WAV, FLAC, M4A)
3. Upload begins automatically
4. Once complete, the **Interactive Player** appears
5. Preview tracks and download your stems

